			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				As usual, I post only when I have completed the quest, or <BR>
gained the item. This is a quest item in which <BR>
you must turn in the THEX MALLET (look up how to do the <BR>
Thex Mallet Quest on this awesome site) to Loveal who <BR>
is a Dark Elf in the third quarter of Neriak. The great thing <BR>
about doing the thex mallet quest, is that my group <BR>
had a necro who would run from 3rd floor of befallen back <BR>
up to Kidzean Gix (in west commons just outside befallen dungeon) <BR>
and say the secret words to get the note <BR>
to give to skeleton Lrold on the 1st floor of befallen. Then the <BR>
22th level zombie-Commander Windstream spawns(he ranges in levels) and we would kill him <BR>
for the container for the thex mallet. You can force spawn <BR>
commander windstream over and over this way. Get the thex mallet handle <BR>
and head from the elf skeleton at the bottom of the <BR>
stairs to the third level entrance door, he spawns very quickly and drops either piece each time.<BR>
Now, getting back to the reaper, u must have a Shadow Knight <BR>
turn in the Thex Mallet to Loveal to get it. If a necro turns it in, <BR>
he may get the extremely rare Ring of the Dead. If anyone else turns <BR>
the thex mallet in, they will get a 8th level spell. Good luck.
				</font>
			</td>

